{"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ApplicationRef\/addMainOption(entries:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/applicationref\/addmainoption(entries:)"]}],"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ApplicationRef","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ApplicationRef\/ApplicationProtocol-Implementations"]]},"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","extendedModule":"GIO","title":"addMainOption(entries:)","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"addMainOption","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"entries","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SP","text":"UnsafePointer"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"text":"GOptionEntry","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":">!)","kind":"text"}],"role":"symbol","externalID":"s:3GIO19ApplicationProtocolPAAE13addMainOption7entriesySPySo13_GOptionEntryVGSg_tF::SYNTHESIZED::s:3GIO14ApplicationRefV"},"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"addMainOption"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"entries","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SP","text":"UnsafePointer"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"GOptionEntry"},{"text":">!)","kind":"text"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This function is comparable to "},{"code":"g_option_context_add_main_entries()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"After the commandline arguments are parsed, the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"[Application](\/\/documentation\/gio\/application\/onhandlelocaloptions(flags:handler:) signal will be emitted.  At this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"point, the application can inspect the values pointed to by "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"arg_data"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"in the given "},{"code":"GOptionEntrys","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Unlike [OptionContext](\/\/documentation\/glib\/optioncontext, ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/Application","type":"reference"},{"text":" supports giving a ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"arg_data","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" for a non-callback [OptionEntry](\/\/documentation\/glib\/optionentry.  This results in the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"argument in question being packed into a [VariantDict](\/\/documentation\/glib\/variantdict which is also","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"passed to [Application](\/\/documentation\/gio\/application\/onhandlelocaloptions(flags:handler:), where it can be"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"inspected and modified.  If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"handlesCommandLine"},{"text":" is","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"set, then the resulting dictionary is sent to the primary instance,","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"where ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_application_command_line_get_options_dict()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" will return it."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"As it has been passed outside the process at this point, the types of all"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"values in the options dict must be checked before being used.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This “packing” is done according to the type of the argument –","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"booleans for normal flags, strings for strings, bytestrings for"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"filenames, etc.  The packing only occurs if the flag is given (ie: we"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"do not pack a “false” [Variant](\/\/documentation\/glib\/variant in the case that a flag is missing).","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"In general, it is recommended that all commandline arguments are","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"parsed locally.  The options dictionary should then be used to"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"transmit the result of the parsing to the primary instance, where"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_variant_dict_lookup()"},{"type":"text","text":" can be used.  For local options, it is"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"possible to either use "},{"code":"arg_data","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" in the usual way, or to consult (and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"potentially remove) the option from the options dictionary.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This function is new in GLib 2.40.  Before then, the only real choice"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"was to send all of the commandline arguments (options and all) to the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"primary instance for handling.  "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/Application"},{"text":" ignored them completely","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"on the local side.  Calling this function “opts in” to the new"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"behaviour, and in particular, means that unrecognized options will be"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"treated as errors.  Unrecognized options have never been ignored when","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"handlesCommandLine","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is unset.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If [Application](\/\/documentation\/gio\/application\/onhandlelocaloptions(flags:handler:) needs to see the list of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"filenames, then the use of [OPTION_REMAINING](\/\/documentation\/glib\/option_remaining is recommended.  If"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"arg_data","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is "},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" then [OPTION_REMAINING](\/\/documentation\/glib\/option_remaining can be used as a key into"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the options dictionary.  If you do use [OPTION_REMAINING](\/\/documentation\/glib\/option_remaining then you"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"need to handle these arguments for yourself because once they are"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"consumed, they will no longer be visible to the default handling","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"(which treats them as filenames to be opened).","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"It is important to use the proper GVariant format when retrieving","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the options with "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_variant_dict_lookup()"},{"type":"text","text":":"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"for ","type":"text"},{"code":"none","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", use ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"b"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"for [string](\/\/documentation\/glib\/string, use "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"&s"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"for [CInt](\/\/documentation\/glib\/cint, use ","type":"text"},{"code":"i","type":"codeVoice"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"for [int64](\/\/documentation\/glib\/int64, use ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"x"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"for [CDouble](\/\/documentation\/glib\/cdouble, use ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"d"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"for [String](\/\/documentation\/glib\/string, use "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"^&ay"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"for [string_array](\/\/documentation\/glib\/string_array, use "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"^a&s"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"for [filename_array](\/\/documentation\/glib\/filename_array, use "},{"code":"^a&ay","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]}]}],"abstract":[{"text":"Adds main option entries to be handled by ","type":"text"},{"code":"application","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"references":{"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/ApplicationRef/ApplicationProtocol-Implementations":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ApplicationRef\/ApplicationProtocol-Implementations","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/applicationref\/applicationprotocol-implementations","type":"topic","title":"ApplicationProtocol Implementations","role":"collectionGroup","kind":"article","abstract":[]},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/ApplicationRef/addMainOption(entries:)":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"addMainOption"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"entries","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:SP","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UnsafePointer"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"text":"GOptionEntry","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":">!)"}],"title":"addMainOption(entries:)","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ApplicationRef\/addMainOption(entries:)","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Adds main option entries to be handled by "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"application"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/gio\/applicationref\/addmainoption(entries:)"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/ApplicationRef":{"type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"ApplicationRef","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ApplicationRef","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/applicationref","title":"ApplicationRef","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"ApplicationRef"}],"abstract":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GApplication"},{"text":" is the core class for application support.","type":"text"}]},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO":{"type":"topic","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","title":"GIO","url":"\/documentation\/gio","role":"collection","kind":"symbol"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/Application":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"Application"}],"title":"Application","abstract":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GApplication"},{"type":"text","text":" is the core class for application support."}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Application","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/Application","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/application"}}}